\item Duchemin, L., Eggers, J., Josserand, C., 2003. Inviscid coalescence of drop. J. Fluid Mech. 487, 167-178.
\item Dupont, J.-B., Legendre, D., 2010. Numerical simulation of static and sliding drop with contact angle hysteresis. Jal Comput. Phys.,229, p. 2453.
\item Ledesma-Alonso, R., Tordjeman, P., Legendre, D., 2012. Multiscale deformation of a liquid surface in interaction with a nanoprobe. Physical Review E 85, 061602.
\item Ledesma-Alonso, R., Legendre, D., Tordjeman, P., 2013. AFM tip effect on a thin liquid film. Langmuir 29, 7749-7757.
\item Rekvig, L., Hafskjold, B., Smit, B., 2004. Molecular simulations of film rupture in Oil/Water/Surfactant systems. Langmuir 20, 11583-11593.
\item Renardy, Y.Y., Renardy, M., Cristini, V., 2001. A new volume-of-fluid formulation for surfactants and simulations of drop deformation under shear at a low viscosity ratio. European Journal of Mechanics. B. Fluids 21, 49–59.
\item Vioque-Martinez, E., Charton, S., Climent, E., Legendre, D., 2016. Numerical simulation of droplet coalescence : Status and main issues. Proceedings DEFI, Solaize
\item Bacle, A., Gautier, R., Jackson, C. L., Fuchs, P. F.J. \& Vanni, S. Interdigitation between Triglycerides and Lipids Modulates Surface Properties of Lipid Droplets. 1417–1430 (2017)
\item Friedman, R.,  et al. Understanding Conformational Dynamics of Complex Lipid Mixtures Relevant to Biology, Journal of Membrane Biology, 251, 5-6, 609-631 (2018)
